videos.description: Kyle Washington goes up for the monster two-handed dunk, but Malcom Bernard comes out of nowhere to make the swat from behind for Xavier.
videos.headline: Xavier's Bernard swats away Washington's huge dunk attempt

videos.description: Jacob Evans uses the nice crossover to create space and hit the jumper while getting fouled.
videos.headline: Evans uses the nice crossover and hits and-1 jumper

videos.description: Xavier's Trevon Bluiett is having a half to remember, posting up 26 points in the first half, including this monster dunk against Cincinnati.
videos.headline: Xavier's Bluiett punctuates huge first half with power dunk

videos.description: Edmond Sumner leaves the rim with hurt feelings after throwing down a vicious hammer dunk to quiet the Cincinnati crowd in the Crosstown Shootout.
videos.headline: Xavier's Sumner nearly destroys the rim with hammer dunk

videos.description: Jarron Cumberland goes end to end and makes the and-1 layup to put Cincinnati on top.
videos.headline: Cumberland goes coast to coast for the layup

videos.description: Jarron Cumberland drives, makes the runner and gets fouled.
videos.headline: Cumberland makes the runner and gets fouled

videos.description: Troy Caupain finally gets his first career win over Xavier thanks to the shooter's roll on the 3-pointer in Cincinnati's victory.
videos.headline: Caupain gets shooter's roll for game-sealing 3-pointer
